original: Burström, Per Oilof Hugo> tandiläka-re, Växjö, f. 24/4/01 i Luleå av disp. Gustaf B. o. Therèse Bäckström. G. 29 m. Lisa Bergquist. Barn: Folke f. 31, Olov 34, Elisabet 37, Kerstin 46. — Stud:ex. i Luleå 21, med. kand. 26, tandl. 29. Prakt, i Växjö sed. 30.
translated: Burström, Per Oilof Hugo, dentist, Växjö, born April 24th, 1901 in Luleå to Gustaf B. and Therèse Bäckström. Married to Lisa Bergquist in 1929. Children: Folke born in 1931, Olov in 1934, Elisabet in 1937, and Kerstin in 1946. Per graduated high school in Luleå in 1921, received his medical degree in 1926, and became a dentist in 1929. He has been practicing in Växjö since 1930.
